snippet.title: Gameplay Trailer - Dead Dock Protocol - Holodock - Wishlist Today!!!!!
snippet.description:
Wishlist Today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3074330/Dead_Dock_Protocol/

Are you ready for the Zombot Outbreak? Get ready to practice your Zombot killing skills in the DDP Holodock demo, which is coming soon for free. Prepare yourself in the Holodock and prepare for the real deal this winter with the release of Dead Dock Protocol coming out for Steam and Steam Deck. 

Check our site for more info: www.deaddockprotocol.com
Developed by Studio 1979
